<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>StaySmart — Vuelos y Transporte</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.staysmartrealty.com">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, #102a45 0%, #050c14 70%);
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(rgba(0,242,254,0.05) 2px, transparent 4px), radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 3px);
            background-size: 80px 80px, 40px 40px;
            background-position: 0 0, 20px 20px;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .glow-bg {
            position: absolute; top: 15%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
            width: 500px; height: 250px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,242,254,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(5, 12, 20, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
        }

        .back-link {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .back-link:hover { color: #00f2fe; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,242,254,0.5); }

        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            z-index: 5;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .brand-logo-area { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .brand-logo-area img { width: 90px; margin-bottom: 15px; }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00f2fe 0%, #4facfe 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .intro {
            max-width: 600px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 45px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 25px;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 35px 30px;
            width: 320px;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #00f2fe;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,242,254,0.1);
        }

        .service-card i { font-size: 2rem; color: #00f2fe; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .service-card h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .service-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 25px; flex-grow: 1; }

        .action-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00f2fe 0%, #4facfe 100%);
            color: #050c14;
            border: none;
            padding: 13px 26px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .action-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,242,254,0.4);
        }

        .note {
            margin-top: 35px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            max-width: 550px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="glow-bg"></div>

    <header>
        <a href="index.html" class="back-link">&larr; Volver a StaySmart</a>
    </header>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="brand-logo-area">
            <img src="Logo-staysmart.png" alt="StaySmart Logo">
        </div>

        <h1>Vuelos y Transporte</h1>
        <p class="intro">
            Encuentra los mejores precios en tiquetes aéreos y alquiler de vehículos para tu próximo viaje.
            Elige tu destino y fechas directamente en la plataforma de nuestro aliado.
        </p>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plane"></i>
                    <h2>Tiquetes Aéreos</h2>
                    <p>Compara vuelos y encuentra las mejores tarifas con Aviasales.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="https://aviasales.tpk.lv/HmacGsQs" class="action-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buscar Vuelos</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-car"></i>
                    <h2>Alquiler de Vehículo</h2>
                    <p>Renta tu auto con las mejores condiciones a través de GetRentacar.com.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="https://getrentacar.tpk.lv/qoq1pzmU" class="action-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buscar Auto</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="note">Al hacer clic entrarás a la plataforma de nuestro aliado, donde podrás ingresar tu destino, fechas y completar tu reserva directamente.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
